er for JPA\n- Implements all TradeServices methods\n- Buy/sell order processing\n- Market summary integration\n- Quote price updates with JMS publishing\n- 619 lines total\n\n---\n\n## 8. MarketSummarySingleton.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/MarketSummarySingleton.java`\n\nSingleton EJB with:\n- @Singleton annotation\n- @Schedule method to update market summary every 20 seconds\n- Calculates TSIA (Trade Stock Index Average)\n- Identifies top gainers/losers\n- CDI event firing for updates\n- Read/write locks\n- 139 lines total\n\n---\n\n## 9. JAXRSApplication.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/jaxrs/JAXRSApplication.java`\n\nJAX-RS application configuration:\n- @ApplicationPath(\"/rest\")\n- Extends javax.ws.rs.core.Application\n- 28 lines total\n\n---\n\n## 10. QuoteResource.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/jaxrs/QuoteResource.java`\n\nREST resource for quotes:\n- @Path(\"quotes\")\n- @RequestScoped\n- GET and POST methods to retrieve quotes by symbol\n- CDI injection of TradeServices\n- 85 lines total\n\n---\n\n## 11. BroadcastResource.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/jaxrs/BroadcastResource.java`\n\nSSE (Server-Sent Events) resource:\n- @ApplicationScoped\n- Broadcasts quote price changes\n- Uses SseBroadcaster\n- Observes async CDI events (@ObservesAsync)\n- 71 lines total\n\n---\n\n## 12. TradeConfig.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/TradeConfig.java`\n\nConfiguration utility class with:\n- Runtime mode constants (EJB3, DIRECT, SESSION_TO_DIRECT)\n- Order processing modes (SYNCH, ASYNCH, ASYNCH_2PHASE)\n- Database parameters (MAX_USERS, MAX_QUOTES)\n- Trading scenario configuration\n- Random data generation utilities\n- 753 lines total\n\n---\n\n## 13. TradeAppJSF.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/jsf/TradeAppJSF.java`\n\nJSF managed bean:\n- @Named(\"tradeapp\"), @SessionScoped\n- Handles login/logout/register/updateProfile operations\n- Validation annotations on fields\n- CDI injection of TradeServices\n- 299 lines total\n\n---\n\n## 14. MarketSummaryDataBean.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/beans/MarketSummaryDataBean.java`\n\nData bean for market summary:\n- Fields: TSIA, openTSIA, volume, topGainers, topLosers, summaryDate\n- Methods: toString(), toHTML(), toJSON()\n- Not a JPA entity - plain data transfer object\n- 287 lines total\n\n---\n\n## 15. TradeDirect.java\n**Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/direct/TradeDirect.java`\n\nDirect JDBC implementation:\n- @Dependent, @TradeJDBC annotations\n- Uses DataSource for direct JDBC access\n- JMS for messaging\n- UserTransaction for transaction management\n- All SQL statements as static constants\n- Complete JDBC implementation of TradeServices\n- 1838 lines total (longest file)\n\n---\n\nAll files use **javax.*** packages (Java EE/Jakarta EE 8 namespace), not jakarta.* packages. These are the exact, complete contents of each file."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"40640270-7dba-44a6-9773-cfde29fa9f25","uuid":"c7792e8d-4916-414f-9d61-80041fb6b7c6"}
