{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_014pso4mD6P5FbUhqS24MDmz","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've successfully created a new pom.xml file for the Spring Boot 3.2.x DayTrader application. Here's a summary of what was included:\n\n## Complete pom.xml Created at:\n**File Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/pom.xml`\n\n## Key Configuration Details:\n\n### Project Metadata:\n- **Parent:** spring-boot-starter-parent 3.2.5\n- **GroupId:** io.openliberty.samples\n- **ArtifactId:** io.openliberty.sample.daytrader8\n- **Version:** 1.0-SNAPSHOT\n- **Packaging:** jar\n- **Java Version:** 21\n\n### Dependencies Included:\n\n1. **Spring Boot Starters:**\n   - `spring-boot-starter-web` (embedded Tomcat + Spring MVC)\n   - `spring-boot-starter-data-jpa` (Spring Data JPA with Hibernate)\n   - `spring-boot-starter-validation` (Bean Validation)\n\n2. **JSP and JSTL Support:**\n   - `spring-boot-starter-tomcat`\n   - `tomcat-embed-jasper` (for JSP compilation)\n   - `jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-api`\n   - `org.glassfish.web:jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl`\n   - `taglibs-standard-spec:1.2.5`\n   - `taglibs-standard-impl:1.2.5`\n\n3. **JSON Processing:**\n   - `jackson-databind`\n\n4. **Database:**\n   - `h2` (runtime scope)\n\n5. **Testing:**\n   - `spring-boot-starter-test` (test scope)\n\n### Build Configuration:\n- `spring-boot-maven-plugin` configured for packaging and running the application\n\nThe pom.xml has been completely rewritten and is now ready for the Spring Boot 3.2.5 migration of the DayTrader application with full support for Jakarta EE APIs, JSP/JSTL, and all required dependencies."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"40640270-7dba-44a6-9773-cfde29fa9f25","uuid":"a3cb8d44-b569-468c-b7b4-716b1c3a6028"}
