{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01PuqYzqos9DJZYQXBBnkswZ","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All the edits have been successfully applied. Let me create a summary of the changes made:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\nI have successfully migrated all five Jakarta EE entity files to Spring Boot 3.2.5 by replacing all `javax.*` imports with `jakarta.*` equivalents. Here's a detailed breakdown of the changes:\n\n### 1. AccountDataBean.java\n**File Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/entities/AccountDataBean.java`\n\n**Changes Made:**\n- Replaced `javax.persistence.*` with `jakarta.persistence.*` (14 imports)\n- Replaced `javax.validation.*` with `jakarta.validation.*` (3 imports)\n- Removed `javax.ejb.EJBException` import\n- Replaced `throw new EJBException(error)` with `throw new RuntimeException(error)` in the `login()` method (line 253)\n\n### 2. AccountProfileDataBean.java\n**File Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/entities/AccountProfileDataBean.java`\n\n**Changes Made:**\n- Replaced `javax.persistence.*` with `jakarta.persistence.*` (5 imports)\n- Replaced `javax.validation.*` with `jakarta.validation.*` (3 imports)\n\n### 3. HoldingDataBean.java\n**File Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/entities/HoldingDataBean.java`\n\n**Changes Made:**\n- Replaced `javax.persistence.*` with `jakarta.persistence.*` (13 imports)\n- Replaced `javax.validation.*` with `jakarta.validation.*` (3 imports)\n\n### 4. OrderDataBean.java\n**File Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/entities/OrderDataBean.java`\n\n**Changes Made:**\n- Replaced `javax.persistence.*` with `jakarta.persistence.*` (15 imports)\n- Replaced `javax.validation.*` with `jakarta.validation.*` (4 imports)\n\n### 5. QuoteDataBean.java\n**File Path:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/entities/QuoteDataBean.java`\n\n**Changes Made:**\n- Replaced `javax.persistence.*` with `jakarta.persistence.*` (8 imports)\n- Replaced `javax.validation.*` with `jakarta.validation.*` (3 imports)\n\n## Summary of Replacements\n\nAll entity files have been successfully migrated with the following package replacements:\n\n- **javax.persistence.*** → **jakarta.persistence.***\n  - Includes: `@Entity`, `@Table`, `@Id`, `@Column`, `@GeneratedValue`, `@OneToOne`, `@OneToMany`, `@ManyToOne`, `@JoinColumn`, `@Temporal`, `@Transient`, `@NamedQueries`, `@NamedQuery`, `@NamedNativeQueries`, `@NamedNativeQuery`, `@TableGenerator`, and related types\n\n- **javax.validation.*** → **jakarta.validation.***\n  - Includes: `@NotNull`, `@NotBlank`, `@Email`, `@PastOrPresent`, `@Positive`, `@PositiveOrZero`\n\n- **javax.ejb.EJBException** → **RuntimeException**\n  - Removed EJB dependency entirely as Spring Boot doesn't use EJB\n  - Updated exception throw in `AccountDataBean.login()` method\n\nAll files are now compatible with Spring Boot 3.2.5's Jakarta EE 9+ namespace requirements."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"40640270-7dba-44a6-9773-cfde29fa9f25","uuid":"84ca2be7-e844-4a12-870f-d79d786cf814"}
