{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_012aMR5A3KkRzkkSfc9EdGWg","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully migrated all the Jakarta EE MDB and JAX-RS classes to Spring Boot 3.2.5 equivalents. Here's a summary of the changes made:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\n### 1. DTBroker3MDB.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/mdb/DTBroker3MDB.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Removed all JMS and EJB imports (`javax.jms.*`, `javax.ejb.*`)\n- Removed `@MessageDriven` annotation and replaced with `@Component`\n- Removed `MessageListener` interface implementation\n- Changed `@Inject` to `@Autowired` for TradeServices injection\n- Simplified injection by removing CDI `Instance<TradeServices>` pattern\n- Converted `onMessage(Message message)` to `processOrder()` method with explicit parameters\n- Replaced `MessageDrivenContext.setRollbackOnly()` with throwing `RuntimeException`\n- Added `@Transactional` annotation for transaction management\n- Kept all business logic intact (order completion, statistics tracking)\n\n### 2. DTStreamer3MDB.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/mdb/DTStreamer3MDB.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Removed all JMS and EJB imports\n- Removed `@MessageDriven` annotation and replaced with `@Component`\n- Removed `MessageListener` interface implementation\n- Converted `onMessage(Message message)` to `processQuoteUpdate()` method with explicit parameters (command, symbol, price, oldPrice, publishTime)\n- Replaced rollback logic with `RuntimeException` throwing\n- Added `@Transactional` annotation\n- Kept statistics tracking and business logic intact\n\n### 3. JAXRSApplication.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/jaxrs/JAXRSApplication.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Removed `@ApplicationPath(\"/rest\")` annotation\n- Removed `extends Application`\n- Marked class as `@Deprecated` with documentation explaining it's not needed in Spring Boot\n- Added comment explaining REST configuration is handled by Spring MVC through `@RestController` classes\n\n### 4. QuoteResource.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/jaxrs/QuoteResource.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced JAX-RS imports with Spring Web imports\n- Changed `@Path(\"quotes\")` to `@RestController` + `@RequestMapping(\"/rest/quotes\")`\n- Removed `@RequestScoped` (Spring controllers are singletons by default)\n- Changed `@GET` to `@GetMapping` with produces parameter\n- Changed `@POST` to `@PostMapping` with consumes/produces parameters\n- Changed `@PathParam` to `@PathVariable`\n- Changed `@FormParam` to `@RequestParam`\n- Simplified injection from CDI `Instance<TradeServices>` to direct `@Autowired TradeServices`\n- Removed constructor injection complexity, using field injection instead\n- Kept all business logic for quote retrieval intact\n\n### 5. BroadcastResource.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/jaxrs/BroadcastResource.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced JAX-RS SSE with Spring's `SseEmitter`\n- Changed `@Path(\"broadcastevents\")` to `@RestController` + `@RequestMapping(\"/rest/broadcastevents\")`\n- Removed `@ApplicationScoped` (not needed in Spring)\n- Removed JAX-RS SSE classes (`SseBroadcaster`, `SseEventSink`, `Sse`, `Builder`)\n- Implemented manual emitter management using `CopyOnWriteArrayList<SseEmitter>`\n- Changed `@ObservesAsync` to `@EventListener` with `@Async` for asynchronous event handling\n- Updated `register()` method to return `SseEmitter` and manage lifecycle (completion, timeout, error)\n- Converted CDI event observer to Spring event listener\n- Changed from `@Context` injection to `@Autowired` for RecentQuotePriceChangeList\n\n## Key Migration Patterns Applied\n\n1. **MDB to Component**: Message-Driven Beans became simple Spring `@Component` classes with public methods\n2. **JAX-RS to Spring MVC**: JAX-RS annotations mapped to Spring Web annotations\n3. **CDI to Spring DI**: `@Inject` became `@Autowired`, removed complex CDI patterns\n4. **SSE**: JAX-RS SSE became Spring's `SseEmitter` with manual emitter lifecycle management\n5. **Events**: CDI `@ObservesAsync` became Spring `@EventListener` with `@Async`\n6. **Transactions**: EJB transaction management became Spring's `@Transactional`\n\nAll business logic has been preserved while adapting to Spring Boot's programming model."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"40640270-7dba-44a6-9773-cfde29fa9f25","uuid":"a3169a44-d29f-4d02-8976-af41f8e69391"}
