{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01URd6K5Gd3Jmg7689joLWC4","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"There are many compilation errors from files that weren't fully migrated. The issues fall into several categories:\n\n1. **jakarta.json doesn't exist** - Need to add JSON-P (Jakarta JSON Processing) dependency or remove those files\n2. **org.springframework.inject doesn't exist** - Wrong imports (should be `@Autowired` not `@Inject`)\n3. **jakarta.faces doesn't exist** - JSF not available in Spring Boot\n4. **jakarta.enterprise.concurrent** - EE Concurrency not in Spring Boot\n5. **jakarta.jms** - JMS not available\n6. **jakarta.xml.bind** - JAXB not included\n7. **javax.servlet references still present**\n8. **Wrong Spring import paths**\n\nThe best strategy: The web/prims, web/servlet, and web/jsf directories contain many demo/test servlets that are not needed for core functionality. I should either fix them all or remove the non-essential ones. Given the number, let me use a pragmatic approach - fix the core ones and remove/exclude the problematic demo files."}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8217,"cache_read_input_tokens":108372,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":8217,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2784},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"40640270-7dba-44a6-9773-cfde29fa9f25","uuid":"e79b1a97-6636-4d06-97ef-74f7ff715ae8"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01URd6K5Gd3Jmg7689joLWC4","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01B2b4rkSpE268gXWRkTH9GY","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Fix all compilation errors batch 1","prompt":"I'm fixing compilation errors in a Jakarta EE to Spring Boot migration. There are many files with wrong imports.\n\nBASE=/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output\n\nThe following errors need to be fixed. For each file, READ it first, then fix it.\n\n## Category 1: Wrong Spring imports (org.springframework.inject doesn't exist, @Inject not in Spring)\n\nThese files have `import org.springframework.inject.*` or `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Inject` which don't exist. Fix them:\n\n1. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeServletAction.java` - Read this file. Fix:\n   - `org.springframework.inject.Any` -> remove (not needed)  \n   - `org.springframework.inject.Instance` -> remove (not needed)\n   - `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Inject` -> `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n   - `org.springframework.context.SessionScoped` -> `org.springframework.web.context.annotation.SessionScope`\n   - `javax.servlet` -> `jakarta.servlet` wherever it still appears\n   - `Instance<TradeServices>` -> `TradeServices` (direct autowiring)\n   - Replace @Inject with @Autowired\n   - Replace @SessionScoped with @SessionScope\n\n2. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeAppServlet.java` - Read and fix:\n   - `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Inject` -> `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n   - `javax.servlet.http` -> `jakarta.servlet.http`\n   - Replace @Inject with @Autowired\n\n3. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TestServlet.java` - Read and fix:\n   - `org.springframework.inject.*` -> remove\n   - `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Inject` -> `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n   - `Instance<TradeServices>` -> `TradeServices`\n   - @Inject -> @Autowired\n\n4. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/OrdersAlertFilter.java` - Read and fix:\n   - Same pattern - fix Spring imports\n   - `Instance<TradeServices>` -> `TradeServices`\n   - @Inject -> @Autowired\n\n5. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeConfigServlet.java` - Read and fix:\n   - @Inject -> @Autowired\n\n6. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeScenarioServlet.java` - Read and fix:\n   - `javax.servlet.http` -> `jakarta.servlet.http`\n\n7. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeWebContextListener.java` - Read and fix:\n   - Remove jakarta.faces imports (JSF not in Spring Boot)\n   - Remove @FacesConfig annotation\n   - Keep as a simple ServletContextListener\n\n## Category 2: EJB annotation mapped wrong\n\n8. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/ejb3/PingServlet2Session2CMROne2One.java` - Read and fix:\n   - `org.springframework.stereotype.EJB` doesn't exist. Replace with `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n   - @EJB -> @Autowired\n\n9. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/ejb3/PingServlet2Session2Entity.java` - Same fix\n10. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/ejb3/PingServlet2Session2Entity2JSP.java` - Same fix\n11. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/ejb3/PingServlet2Session2EntityCollection.java` - Same fix\n12. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/ejb3/PingServlet2MDBQueue.java` - Read and rewrite to remove JMS. Just make the servlet log a message instead.\n\nFor each file, read it first then make the corrections.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8217,"cache_read_input_tokens":108372,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":8217,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2784},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"40640270-7dba-44a6-9773-cfde29fa9f25","uuid":"5f2a712c-8e5d-4d32-adae-7094cbf132e4"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01URd6K5Gd3Jmg7689joLWC4","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01JbiTNr6WMQJtR55grWcfkZ","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Fix compilation errors batch 2","prompt":"I'm fixing compilation errors in a Jakarta EE to Spring Boot migration.\n\nBASE=/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output\n\nFix these files. For each file, READ it first, then fix it:\n\n## Category 3: jakarta.json does not exist (JSON-P not in Spring Boot)\n\nThese files use jakarta.json (JSON Processing API) which isn't included in Spring Boot. Replace with simple string building or Jackson.\n\n1. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/websocket/ActionMessage.java` - Replace jakarta.json with simple string parsing or Jackson\n2. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/websocket/MarketSummaryWebSocket.java` - Remove jakarta.json usage\n3. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/websocket/JsonEncoder.java` - Replace with Jackson or simple toString\n4. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/websocket/JsonDecoder.java` - Replace with Jackson or simple parsing\n5. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/websocket/QuotePriceChangeListEncoder.java` - Replace with Jackson\n6. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/PingJSONPStreaming.java` - Replace jakarta.json with simple string output\n7. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/PingJSONPObject.java` - Replace jakarta.json with simple string output\n8. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/PingJSONPObjectFactory.java` - Replace jakarta.json with simple string output\n\n## Category 4: jakarta.faces (JSF not in Spring Boot)\n9. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/jsf/LoginValidator.java` - Remove JSF-specific Validator interface. Make it a simple POJO validator without jakarta.faces dependencies. Just keep a public validate() method that throws Exception.\n\n## Category 5: jakarta.enterprise.concurrent (EE Concurrency not in Spring Boot)\n10. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/PingManagedThread.java` - Replace ManagedThreadFactory with standard Java Thread creation\n11. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/PingManagedExecutor.java` - Replace ManagedExecutorService with standard Java ExecutorService\n12. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/PingWebSocketJson.java` - Replace both ManagedExecutorService and jakarta.json\n\n## Category 6: jakarta.xml.bind (JAXB not in Spring Boot by default)\n13. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/jaxrs/XMLObject.java` - Remove @XmlRootElement, just keep as plain POJO\n14. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/jaxrs/ObjectFactory.java` - Remove @XmlRegistry, just keep as plain factory\n\n## Category 7: CDI-specific classes\n15. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/cdi/PingInterceptorBinding.java` - Remove InterceptorBinding. Just make it a simple annotation with @Target and @Retention.\n16. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/cdi/CDIEventProducer.java` - Replace CDI Event with Spring ApplicationEventPublisher. Replace ManagedExecutorService with standard ExecutorService. Replace @ApplicationScoped with @Component.\n17. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/cdi/PingServletCDIEvent.java` - Replace CDI @Observes with Spring @EventListener or just a method annotation.\n\nFor each file: read it first, then make the fix.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8217,"cache_read_input_tokens":108372,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":8217,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2784},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"40640270-7dba-44a6-9773-cfde29fa9f25","uuid":"43deb177-7eb9-47e5-9a86-38763de6a0b1"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'm fixing compilation errors in a Jakarta EE to Spring Boot migration. There are many files with wrong imports.\n\nBASE=/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output\n\nThe following errors need to be fixed. For each file, READ it first, then fix it.\n\n## Category 1: Wrong Spring imports (org.springframework.inject doesn't exist, @Inject not in Spring)\n\nThese files have `import org.springframework.inject.*` or `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Inject` which don't exist. Fix them:\n\n1. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeServletAction.java` - Read this file. Fix:\n   - `org.springframework.inject.Any` -> remove (not needed)  \n   - `org.springframework.inject.Instance` -> remove (not needed)\n   - `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Inject` -> `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n   - `org.springframework.context.SessionScoped` -> `org.springframework.web.context.annotation.SessionScope`\n   - `javax.servlet` -> `jakarta.servlet` wherever it still appears\n   - `Instance<TradeServices>` -> `TradeServices` (direct autowiring)\n   - Replace @Inject with @Autowired\n   - Replace @SessionScoped with @SessionScope\n\n2. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeAppServlet.java` - Read and fix:\n   - `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Inject` -> `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n   - `javax.servlet.http` -> `jakarta.servlet.http`\n   - Replace @Inject with @Autowired\n\n3. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TestServlet.java` - Read and fix:\n   - `org.springframework.inject.*` -> remove\n   - `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Inject` -> `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n   - `Instance<TradeServices>` -> `TradeServices`\n   - @Inject -> @Autowired\n\n4. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/OrdersAlertFilter.java` - Read and fix:\n   - Same pattern - fix Spring imports\n   - `Instance<TradeServices>` -> `TradeServices`\n   - @Inject -> @Autowired\n\n5. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeConfigServlet.java` - Read and fix:\n   - @Inject -> @Autowired\n\n6. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeScenarioServlet.java` - Read and fix:\n   - `javax.servlet.http` -> `jakarta.servlet.http`\n\n7. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeWebContextListener.java` - Read and fix:\n   - Remove jakarta.faces imports (JSF not in Spring Boot)\n   - Remove @FacesConfig annotation\n   - Keep as a simple ServletContextListener\n\n## Category 2: EJB annotation mapped wrong\n\n8. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/ejb3/PingServlet2Session2CMROne2One.java` - Read and fix:\n   - `org.springframework.stereotype.EJB` doesn't exist. Replace with `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n   - @EJB -> @Autowired\n\n9. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/ejb3/PingServlet2Session2Entity.java` - Same fix\n10. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/ejb3/PingServlet2Session2Entity2JSP.java` - Same fix\n11. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/ejb3/PingServlet2Session2EntityCollection.java` - Same fix\n12. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/ejb3/PingServlet2MDBQueue.java` - Read and rewrite to remove JMS. Just make the servlet log a message instead.\n\nFor each file, read it first then make the corrections."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01B2b4rkSpE268gXWRkTH9GY","session_id":"40640270-7dba-44a6-9773-cfde29fa9f25","uuid":"a0531947-b585-4554-918d-c66025acfaad"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'm fixing compilation errors in a Jakarta EE to Spring Boot migration.\n\nBASE=/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output\n\nFix these files. For each file, READ it first, then fix it:\n\n## Category 3: jakarta.json does not exist (JSON-P not in Spring Boot)\n\nThese files use jakarta.json (JSON Processing API) which isn't included in Spring Boot. Replace with simple string building or Jackson.\n\n1. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/websocket/ActionMessage.java` - Replace jakarta.json with simple string parsing or Jackson\n2. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/websocket/MarketSummaryWebSocket.java` - Remove jakarta.json usage\n3. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/websocket/JsonEncoder.java` - Replace with Jackson or simple toString\n4. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/websocket/JsonDecoder.java` - Replace with Jackson or simple parsing\n5. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/websocket/QuotePriceChangeListEncoder.java` - Replace with Jackson\n6. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/PingJSONPStreaming.java` - Replace jakarta.json with simple string output\n7. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/PingJSONPObject.java` - Replace jakarta.json with simple string output\n8. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/PingJSONPObjectFactory.java` - Replace jakarta.json with simple string output\n\n## Category 4: jakarta.faces (JSF not in Spring Boot)\n9. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/jsf/LoginValidator.java` - Remove JSF-specific Validator interface. Make it a simple POJO validator without jakarta.faces dependencies. Just keep a public validate() method that throws Exception.\n\n## Category 5: jakarta.enterprise.concurrent (EE Concurrency not in Spring Boot)\n10. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/PingManagedThread.java` - Replace ManagedThreadFactory with standard Java Thread creation\n11. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/PingManagedExecutor.java` - Replace ManagedExecutorService with standard Java ExecutorService\n12. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/PingWebSocketJson.java` - Replace both ManagedExecutorService and jakarta.json\n\n## Category 6: jakarta.xml.bind (JAXB not in Spring Boot by default)\n13. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/jaxrs/XMLObject.java` - Remove @XmlRootElement, just keep as plain POJO\n14. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/jaxrs/ObjectFactory.java` - Remove @XmlRegistry, just keep as plain factory\n\n## Category 7: CDI-specific classes\n15. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/cdi/PingInterceptorBinding.java` - Remove InterceptorBinding. Just make it a simple annotation with @Target and @Retention.\n16. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/cdi/CDIEventProducer.java` - Replace CDI Event with Spring ApplicationEventPublisher. Replace ManagedExecutorService with standard ExecutorService. Replace @ApplicationScoped with @Component.\n17. `$BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/cdi/PingServletCDIEvent.java` - Replace CDI @Observes with Spring @EventListener or just a method annotation.\n\nFor each file: read it first, then make the fix."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01JbiTNr6WMQJtR55grWcfkZ","session_id":"40640270-7dba-44a6-9773-cfde29fa9f25","uuid":"698774d9-a0fd-45d0-9697-b9c6104aecc6"}
