{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01W2ncjvpDvX2env9o7iBmBE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01RERKufBWhyK24JRvqWUg7g","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Fix remaining compile errors","prompt":"Fix remaining compilation errors in the Spring Boot migration. For each file, READ it first, then fix it.\n\nBASE=/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output\n\n## Remaining errors to fix:\n\n1. **TradeServletAction.java** - still has `javax.servlet` references in method signatures AND `javax.ejb` reference\n   - Read $BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeServletAction.java\n   - Replace ALL remaining `javax.servlet` with `jakarta.servlet` \n   - Replace `javax.ejb` with just remove it or use RuntimeException\n\n2. **TradeConfigServlet.java** - has `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Inject` which doesn't exist\n   - Read $BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeConfigServlet.java\n   - Replace `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Inject;` with `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;`\n   - Replace `@Inject` annotation with `@Autowired`\n\n3. **PingServlet2MDBTopic.java** - still uses jakarta.jms which doesn't exist in Spring Boot\n   - Read $BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/ejb3/PingServlet2MDBTopic.java\n   - Rewrite to remove all JMS code. Replace with a simple servlet that just logs a message (same pattern as PingServlet2MDBQueue was fixed)\n\n4. **PingServletCDIEventAsync.java** - uses ObservesAsync and Interceptor from wrong packages\n   - Read $BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/cdi/PingServletCDIEventAsync.java\n   - Replace `org.springframework.context.event.ObservesAsync` -> use `@EventListener` and `@Async` instead\n   - Replace `org.springframework.stereotype.Interceptor` -> remove, not needed\n   - The methods with @ObservesAsync should be changed to @EventListener methods\n\n5. **JAXRSSyncService.java** - still uses jakarta.ws.rs which doesn't exist in Spring Boot  \n   - Read $BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/jaxrs/JAXRSSyncService.java\n   - Convert from JAX-RS to Spring @RestController\n   - Replace @Path, @GET, @POST, @QueryParam, @Produces, @Consumes with Spring equivalents\n   - Replace @ApplicationPath with @RequestMapping\n\n6. **TradeRunTimeModeLiteral.java** - implements Annotation interface but doesn't provide annotationType() method\n   - Read $BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/TradeRunTimeModeLiteral.java\n   - Add the `annotationType()` method that returns RuntimeMode.class\n   - Or remove the `implements RuntimeMode` and just make it a plain class with a value() method\n\nFor EACH file: read it first, then apply the fix.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6229,"cache_read_input_tokens":124426,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":6229,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":927},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"40640270-7dba-44a6-9773-cfde29fa9f25","uuid":"e3159a6c-e4fa-4220-8a3b-9315ee5d5eba"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Fix remaining compilation errors in the Spring Boot migration. For each file, READ it first, then fix it.\n\nBASE=/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output\n\n## Remaining errors to fix:\n\n1. **TradeServletAction.java** - still has `javax.servlet` references in method signatures AND `javax.ejb` reference\n   - Read $BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeServletAction.java\n   - Replace ALL remaining `javax.servlet` with `jakarta.servlet` \n   - Replace `javax.ejb` with just remove it or use RuntimeException\n\n2. **TradeConfigServlet.java** - has `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Inject` which doesn't exist\n   - Read $BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeConfigServlet.java\n   - Replace `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Inject;` with `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;`\n   - Replace `@Inject` annotation with `@Autowired`\n\n3. **PingServlet2MDBTopic.java** - still uses jakarta.jms which doesn't exist in Spring Boot\n   - Read $BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/ejb3/PingServlet2MDBTopic.java\n   - Rewrite to remove all JMS code. Replace with a simple servlet that just logs a message (same pattern as PingServlet2MDBQueue was fixed)\n\n4. **PingServletCDIEventAsync.java** - uses ObservesAsync and Interceptor from wrong packages\n   - Read $BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/cdi/PingServletCDIEventAsync.java\n   - Replace `org.springframework.context.event.ObservesAsync` -> use `@EventListener` and `@Async` instead\n   - Replace `org.springframework.stereotype.Interceptor` -> remove, not needed\n   - The methods with @ObservesAsync should be changed to @EventListener methods\n\n5. **JAXRSSyncService.java** - still uses jakarta.ws.rs which doesn't exist in Spring Boot  \n   - Read $BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/jaxrs/JAXRSSyncService.java\n   - Convert from JAX-RS to Spring @RestController\n   - Replace @Path, @GET, @POST, @QueryParam, @Produces, @Consumes with Spring equivalents\n   - Replace @ApplicationPath with @RequestMapping\n\n6. **TradeRunTimeModeLiteral.java** - implements Annotation interface but doesn't provide annotationType() method\n   - Read $BASE/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/TradeRunTimeModeLiteral.java\n   - Add the `annotationType()` method that returns RuntimeMode.class\n   - Or remove the `implements RuntimeMode` and just make it a plain class with a value() method\n\nFor EACH file: read it first, then apply the fix."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01RERKufBWhyK24JRvqWUg7g","session_id":"40640270-7dba-44a6-9773-cfde29fa9f25","uuid":"d623fe96-c196-4c28-8a14-b781ce7f2fdb"}
