{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01RERKufBWhyK24JRvqWUg7g","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! The compilation was successful. Let me create a summary of all the fixes I made:\n\n## Summary\n\nI have successfully fixed all 6 remaining compilation errors in the Spring Boot migration. Here's a detailed breakdown of the changes made:\n\n### 1. **TradeServletAction.java** \n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeServletAction.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced all `javax.servlet` references in Javadoc comments with `jakarta.servlet`\n- Replaced all `javax.io.IOException` references with `java.io.IOException`\n- Removed the catch block for `javax.ejb.FinderException` in the `doHome()` method (lines 278-288) since EJB exceptions don't exist in Spring Boot\n\n### 2. **TradeConfigServlet.java**\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/servlet/TradeConfigServlet.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Inject;` with `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;`\n- The `@Inject` annotation was already changed to `@Autowired` on line 46 (no further changes needed)\n\n### 3. **PingServlet2MDBTopic.java**\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/ejb3/PingServlet2MDBTopic.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Removed all JMS-related imports (`jakarta.jms.*`)\n- Removed all JMS-related fields (`ConnectionFactory`, `Topic`)\n- Rewrote the `doGet()` method to remove all JMS code\n- Replaced JMS message posting with simple logging using `Log.log()`\n- Added explanatory comment that JMS/MDB functionality is not available in Spring Boot\n\n### 4. **PingServletCDIEventAsync.java**\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/cdi/PingServletCDIEventAsync.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Removed `import org.springframework.context.event.ObservesAsync;` (doesn't exist in Spring)\n- Removed `import org.springframework.stereotype.Interceptor;` (not needed)\n- Removed `import jakarta.annotation.Priority;`\n- Added proper Spring imports:\n  - `import org.springframework.context.event.EventListener;`\n  - `import org.springframework.core.annotation.Order;`\n  - `import org.springframework.scheduling.annotation.Async;`\n  - `import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;`\n- Added `@Component` annotation to the class\n- Converted `@ObservesAsync` methods to Spring `@EventListener` methods with `@Async` and `@Order` annotations\n- Changed parameter type from `@HitAsync String event` to `CDIEventProducer.HitAsyncEvent event` to use the existing event class\n\n### 5. **JAXRSSyncService.java**\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/web/prims/jaxrs/JAXRSSyncService.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Removed all JAX-RS imports (`jakarta.ws.rs.*`)\n- Added Spring Web MVC imports:\n  - `import org.springframework.http.MediaType;`\n  - `import org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.*;`\n- Replaced `@ApplicationPath` and `@Path` with `@RestController` and `@RequestMapping(\"/jaxrs/sync\")`\n- Replaced `@GET` with `@GetMapping`\n- Replaced `@POST` with `@PostMapping`\n- Replaced `@QueryParam` with `@RequestParam`\n- Replaced `@Produces`/`@Consumes` with Spring's `produces`/`consumes` attributes\n- Renamed the second `echoObject` method to `echoXMLObject` to avoid method signature conflict\n\n### 6. **TradeRunTimeModeLiteral.java**\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/TradeRunTimeModeLiteral.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Added `import java.lang.annotation.Annotation;`\n- Added the required `annotationType()` method that returns `RuntimeMode.class`\n- This method is required because the class implements the `RuntimeMode` annotation interface\n\n## Compilation Result\n\nThe project now compiles successfully with only deprecation warnings (related to legacy Java API usage like `new Integer()`, which are not critical for functionality). All the Spring Boot migration compilation errors have been resolved."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"40640270-7dba-44a6-9773-cfde29fa9f25","uuid":"b672fb4b-d169-40e5-8dfc-c633fc271a3b"}
