{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01F1ZHtw7tPDVvMx7GkDBGKn","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here's a summary of the migration:\n\n## Migration Complete\n\n**DayTrader: Jakarta EE 8 (Open Liberty) -> Spring Boot 3.2.5 (Embedded Tomcat)**\n\n### Final Status: All 4/4 smoke tests passing\n\n### Key changes in this session:\n- **Fixed `OrderDataJSF`**: Added missing `@RequestScope` annotation. The bean was a singleton (`@Controller` without scope), causing its `@PostConstruct` method to call `RequestContextHolder.currentRequestAttributes()` during application startup when no HTTP request context exists. Adding `@RequestScope` ensures it's only created within an active web request, consistent with all other JSF-origin controllers.\n\n### Issues resolved across the entire migration:\n1. Complete pom.xml rewrite (Liberty -> Spring Boot 3.2.5)\n2. ~39 Java source files migrated (EJB -> `@Service`, CDI -> Spring DI, JAX-RS -> `@RestController`, JSF -> `@Controller`, JMS removed)\n3. `javax.*` -> `jakarta.*` namespace migration\n4. 3 rounds of compilation error fixes (~100+ errors)\n5. H2 database URL compatibility fix\n6. Spring bean ambiguity resolution (`@Primary` on `TradeSLSBBean`)\n7. CGLIB proxy fix (private -> protected on `MarketSummarySingleton.updateMarketSummary()`)\n8. `OrderDataJSF` missing `@RequestScope` fix (this session)"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":414,"cache_read_input_tokens":63624,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":414,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":361},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"40640270-7dba-44a6-9773-cfde29fa9f25","uuid":"f37d984b-2a29-42d3-bd69-29a08302836e"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":2974531,"duration_api_ms":3806060,"num_turns":112,"result":"All tasks are complete. Here's a summary of the migration:\n\n## Migration Complete\n\n**DayTrader: Jakarta EE 8 (Open Liberty) -> Spring Boot 3.2.5 (Embedded Tomcat)**\n\n### Final Status: All 4/4 smoke tests passing\n\n### Key changes in this session:\n- **Fixed `OrderDataJSF`**: Added missing `@RequestScope` annotation. The bean was a singleton (`@Controller` without scope), causing its `@PostConstruct` method to call `RequestContextHolder.currentRequestAttributes()` during application startup when no HTTP request context exists. Adding `@RequestScope` ensures it's only created within an active web request, consistent with all other JSF-origin controllers.\n\n### Issues resolved across the entire migration:\n1. Complete pom.xml rewrite (Liberty -> Spring Boot 3.2.5)\n2. ~39 Java source files migrated (EJB -> `@Service`, CDI -> Spring DI, JAX-RS -> `@RestController`, JSF -> `@Controller`, JMS removed)\n3. `javax.*` -> `jakarta.*` namespace migration\n4. 3 rounds of compilation error fixes (~100+ errors)\n5. H2 database URL compatibility fix\n6. Spring bean ambiguity resolution (`@Primary` on `TradeSLSBBean`)\n7. CGLIB proxy fix (private -> protected on `MarketSummarySingleton.updateMarketSummary()`)\n8. `OrderDataJSF` missing `@RequestScope` fix (this session)","session_id":"40640270-7dba-44a6-9773-cfde29fa9f25","total_cost_usd":34.32251663999999,"usage":{"input_tokens":5232,"cache_creation_input_tokens":527780,"cache_read_input_tokens":6632379,"output_tokens":36110,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":527780}},"modelUsage":{"aws/claude-3-5-haiku":{"inputTokens":387222,"outputTokens":15164,"cacheReadInputTokens":164453,"cacheCreationInputTokens":33246,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.4168358399999999,"contex